{"id":301151,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/06/维权网-安徽宿州五出嫁女为土地承包权赴京上访/","date":"2013-06-28T02:33:24Z","modified":"2013-06-28T02:33:24Z","title":"维权网 | 安徽宿州五出嫁女为土地承包权赴京上访被拘留（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员周维林报道）安徽省宿州市经济开发区刘合村的五名出嫁女，因在土地二轮承包时被村委会剥夺了土地承包权，从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2004</span><span>年开始，她们为此而上访，历经九年，因政府不作为，无法解决土地承包权，五名出嫁女中的四人于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>到北京上访，在北京美国大使馆附近被北京警方“当场抓获”，在被宿州市截访人员带回后，由宿州市公安局经济开发区分局决定分别行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日的处罚。政府不作为导致出嫁女的权利得不到保障，却对被逼赴京上访的出嫁女给予行政处罚，如此不公，岂能令出嫁女心服，社会和谐必须尊重人权，而人权中男女平等是其中非常重要的内容。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>安徽省宿州市经济开发区的刘合村的土地二轮承包是在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2001</span><span>年开始的，落后于国家规定的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1995</span><span>年土地二轮承包达六年之久，该村的邵敏、刘守芹、刘芳、邵正侠、刘守芹（与前刘守芹重名）五名女性恰在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1995</span><span>年—</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2001</span><span>年期间结婚，而且不是与本村村民结婚，于是刘合村村委会就以她们已经出嫁为由剥夺了她们的土地承包权。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>为此，邵敏、刘守芹、刘芳、邵正侠、刘守芹五出嫁女于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2004</span><span>年开始上访，历经宿州市、安徽省政府信访部门，并向各级妇联求助。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>因为在安徽省信访无果，五出嫁女中的四位邵敏、刘守芹、刘芳、刘守芹于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>到达北京，结果因无意中在美国大使馆附近逗留被北京公安局朝麦子店派出所“当场抓获”，派出所于下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>时将她们四人送久敬庄关押。当晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>时许安徽省驻京办去登记，然后是宿州市驻京办的工作人员到场，称要带她们回去解决问题，可还没说好就令黑保安进屋强行将她们拉出来押上车，连夜送回宿州市。第二天上午到达宿州，警方做完笔录后决定对她们四名出嫁女分别给予拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>天的行政处罚。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>如今，出嫁女们被拘留六天后并没有因此而恐惧，她们维护自身权利的意志更加坚定了，她们绝不同意刘合村委会以“群众”的名义，给的承包地的远少于其他村民的做法。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-63cggPOeNqk/UczdtOfut_I/AAAAAAAAkZA/ESvwrjUj5iQ/s500/%25E5%2588%2598%25E9%2587%2587%25E8%258A%25B9%25E5%2592%258C%25E9%2582%25B5%25E6%2595%258F.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-63cggPOeNqk/UczdtOfut_I/AAAAAAAAkZA/ESvwrjUj5iQ/s320/%25E5%2588%2598%25E9%2587%2587%25E8%258A%25B9%25E5%2592%258C%25E9%2582%25B5%25E6%2595%258F.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>刘采芹和邵敏</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-2U9GDRP3HEc/Uczdgw0JUHI/AAAAAAAAkYU/-UCpGFspWgo/s800/%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F+(19).jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-2U9GDRP3HEc/Uczdgw0JUHI/AAAAAAAAkYU/-UCpGFspWgo/s320/%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F+(19).jpg\" width=\"232\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-phuxaDhB2Fg/Uczdh-z3cAI/AAAAAAAAkYg/COA_YqLcrpg/s800/%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F+(20).jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-phuxaDhB2Fg/Uczdh-z3cAI/AAAAAAAAkYg/COA_YqLcrpg/s320/%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F+(20).jpg\" width=\"232\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-8YCzI9zWt-E/Uczdh2zFhgI/AAAAAAAAkYc/bSBvRN-oN_A/s800/%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F+(21).jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-8YCzI9zWt-E/Uczdh2zFhgI/AAAAAAAAkYc/bSBvRN-oN_A/s800/%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F+(21).jpg\" width=\"232\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ZtB-V_XSmc0/Uczdls-orPI/AAAAAAAAkYs/X5KTjfOW5Tc/s800/%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F+(22).jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ZtB-V_XSmc0/Uczdls-orPI/AAAAAAAAkYs/X5KTjfOW5Tc/s800/%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F+(22).jpg\" width=\"228\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-g8IfcmTgzjc/Uczdsrl40zI/AAAAAAAAkY0/7D8AJgl3l0c/s800/%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F+(23).jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-g8IfcmTgzjc/Uczdsrl40zI/AAAAAAAAkY0/7D8AJgl3l0c/s320/%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F+(23).jpg\" width=\"218\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><span><span></span><span></span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}